despicable me 3 ( 3d : despicable me 3 ) is a 2014 american 3d computer-animated comedy adventure film produced by illumination entertainment . it is the third installment in the despicable me franchise . the film was released on june 30 , 2017 , by universal pictures . despicable me 3 was released on june 30 , 2017 , by universal pictures . despicable me 3 was released on june 30 , 2017 , by universal pictures .